<Layout 
  title="About CCTV Trailer | Mobile Security Solutions Tacoma"
  description="Learn about CCTV Trailer - locally owned mobile surveillance company serving Tacoma and the Pacific Northwest. 20+ years of security expertise, professional service, and weather-resistant trailers."
